---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About — ABM"
  description="ABM (Basit Masood) — Lead Product Designer at ZAR. 6+ years in fintech product design. Founding designer who builds design orgs and products from zero."
  canonicalUrl="https://abmcooks.github.io/about/"
  ogTitle="About — ABM"
  ogDescription="6+ years in fintech product design. Founding designer. Systems, teams, products from zero."
  active="story"
>

<style is:global>
    /* --- WRAPPER --- */
    .wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 48px;
    }

    /* --- ABOUT HERO --- */
    .about-hero {
      padding: 80px 0 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .about-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fu 0.5s 0.2s forwards;
    }

    .about-name {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fu 0.7s 0.4s forwards;
    }

    .about-intro {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-style: italic;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fu 0.6s 0.6s forwards;
    }

    .photo-wrap {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fu 0.8s 0.5s forwards;
    }

    .photo {
      width: 280px;
      max-width: 280px;
      height: 340px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12), 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .photo img {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: right bottom;
      transform: scale(1.2);
      transform-origin: right bottom;
      display: block;
    }

    .photo::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* --- WHO I AM --- */
    .who { padding: 100px 0 0; }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .section-label::before {
      content: '';
      width: 24px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .who-statement {
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--text);
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .who-statement .wh-em { color: var(--red); }

    .who-facts { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }

    .who-fact {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    .who-fact:hover { border-color: rgba(204, 41, 54, 0.15); }
    .who-fact .wf-icon { margin-right: 6px; }

    /* --- JOURNEY TIMELINE --- */
    .journey { padding: 100px 0 0; }

    .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 48px; margin-top: 8px; }

    .timeline::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 7px;
      top: 10px;
      bottom: 10px;
      width: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03));
    }

    .tl-item { position: relative; padding: 0 0 56px; }
    .tl-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }

    .tl-dot {
      position: absolute;
      left: -48px;
      top: 6px;
      width: 15px;
      height: 15px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      background: var(--bg);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .tl-dot::after { content: ''; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .tl-item.current .tl-dot { border-color: var(--red); }
    .tl-item.current .tl-dot::after { background: var(--red); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(204, 41, 54, 0.5); }

    .tl-date { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .tl-company { font-family: var(--body); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .tl-role { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 12px; }

    .tl-desc {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    .tl-desc strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }

    .tl-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 14px; }

    .tl-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      border: 1px solid;
    }

    /* Company colors */
    .tl-zar .tl-company { color: var(--gold); }
    .tl-zar .tl-tag { color: var(--gold); border-color: rgba(196, 173, 84, 0.15); background: rgba(196, 173, 84, 0.04); }
    .tl-adib .tl-company { color: var(--blue); }
    .tl-adib .tl-tag { color: var(--blue); border-color: rgba(0, 58, 120, 0.15); background: rgba(0, 58, 120, 0.04); }
    .tl-sp .tl-company { color: var(--teal); }
    .tl-sp .tl-tag { color: var(--teal); border-color: rgba(255, 123, 102, 0.15); background: rgba(255, 123, 102, 0.04); }
    .tl-xp .tl-company { color: var(--emerald); }
    .tl-xp .tl-tag { color: var(--emerald); border-color: rgba(98, 0, 238, 0.15); background: rgba(98, 0, 238, 0.04); }
    .tl-wtt .tl-company { color: var(--violet); }
    .tl-wtt .tl-tag { color: var(--violet); border-color: rgba(188, 32, 75, 0.15); background: rgba(188, 32, 75, 0.04); }

    /* --- PHILOSOPHY --- */
    .philosophy { padding: 100px 0 0; }
    .phil-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 8px; }

    .phil-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
      padding: 32px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.4s, box-shadow 0.4s;
    }

    .phil-card:hover { border-color: rgba(204, 41, 54, 0.12); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); }

    .phil-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(204, 41, 54, 0.15), transparent);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.4s;
    }

    .phil-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

    .phil-num { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.04em; }
    .phil-title { font-family: var(--body); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .phil-text { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-dim); }

    /* --- LEADERSHIP --- */
    .leadership { padding: 100px 0 0; }

    .lead-quote {
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 36px);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.35;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--text);
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .lead-quote .lq-em { color: var(--red); }

    .lead-body { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 640px; }
    .lead-body p { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .lead-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* --- TESTIMONIAL MARQUEE --- */
    .testimonials {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      margin: 100px 0 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);
    }

    .trow { display: flex; gap: 16px; padding: 8px 0; width: max-content; }
    .trow-left { animation: mql 45s linear infinite; }
    .trow-right { animation: mqr 50s linear infinite; }
    .trow:hover { animation-play-state: paused; }

    .tcard {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 380px;
      padding: 24px 28px;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    .tcard:hover { border-color: rgba(204, 41, 54, 0.1); }
    .tcard .tq { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.65; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .tcard .tq strong { color: var(--text); font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; }
    .tcard .ta { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .tcard .tt { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }

    @keyframes mql { from { transform: translateX(0); } to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }
    @keyframes mqr { from { transform: translateX(-50%); } to { transform: translateX(0); } }

    /* --- STATS --- */
    .stats { padding: 100px 0 0; position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .stats-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .st { padding: 36px 16px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid var(--card-border); position: relative; }
    .st:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .st .sn { font-family: var(--body); font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); }
    .st .sl { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 500; margin-top: 4px; line-height: 1.4; }

    /* --- FOOTER --- */
    footer { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 900px; margin: 100px auto 0; padding: 0 48px; text-align: center; }
    .fb { padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .fb-social { display: flex; gap: 8px; }

    .fbs {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
      background: transparent; color: var(--text-muted);
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .fbs:hover { border-color: rgba(204, 41, 54, 0.3); color: var(--red); }

    /* --- DELAY CLASSES --- */
    .rd1 { transition-delay: .08s; }
    .rd2 { transition-delay: .16s; }
    .rd3 { transition-delay: .24s; }
    .rd4 { transition-delay: .32s; }
    .rd5 { transition-delay: .40s; }
    .rd6 { transition-delay: .48s; }

    /* --- RESPONSIVE --- */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .wrap, footer { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
      .about-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .photo-wrap { order: -1; }
      .photo { width: 180px; height: 220px; }
      .phil-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .st:nth-child(3) { border-right: none; }
      .st:nth-child(1), .st:nth-child(2), .st:nth-child(3) { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border); }
      .tcard { width: 300px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .about-name { font-size: 36px; }
      .who-statement { font-size: 20px; }
      .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .st:nth-child(even) { border-right: none; }
      .st { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border); }
      .st:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .fb { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; text-align: center; }
      .tcard { width: 280px; padding: 20px; }
    }
</style>

  <div class="wrap">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="photo-wrap">
        <div class="photo">
          <img src="/assets/images/about/abm.jpg" alt="ABM — Basit Masood" loading="eager">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="about-label">Story</div>
        <h1 class="about-name">Basit Masood</h1>
        <p class="about-intro">I keep starting over. On purpose.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="who reveal">
      <div class="section-label">Who I Am</div>
      <div class="who-statement">
        Product designer who builds <span class="wh-em">teams, systems, and products</span> at every stage — from
        founding a startup's first design org to leading enterprise banking redesigns. 6+ years in fintech, where a
        single confusing screen means people walk away with their money.
      </div>
      <div class="who-facts">
        <span class="who-fact"><span class="wf-icon">&#127462;&#127466;</span> Dubai, UAE</span>
        <span class="who-fact">Lead Designer at ZAR</span>
        <span class="who-fact">Previously SadaPay, ADIB</span>
        <span class="who-fact">Systems thinker</span>
        <span class="who-fact">Fintech &amp; emerging markets</span>
        <span class="who-fact">Hires &amp; grows teams</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="journey reveal">
      <div class="section-label">Journey</div>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="tl-item current tl-zar reveal rd1">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">2024 — Present</div>
          <div class="tl-company">ZAR</div>
          <div class="tl-role">Lead Product Designer &middot; Founding Designer</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">Solana-based digital dollar wallet backed by a16z. Built the design system from zero, led on-ground user research, redesigned core flows based on behavioral data, and hired the design team.</div>
          <div class="tl-tags">
            <span class="tl-tag">Design System</span>
            <span class="tl-tag">User Research</span>
            <span class="tl-tag">Hiring</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tl-item tl-adib reveal rd2">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">2024 — 2025</div>
          <div class="tl-company">ADIB</div>
          <div class="tl-role">Lead Product Designer</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">One of the world's largest Islamic banks. Delivered the Open Banking experience and Visa Direct remittance product — <strong>the first bank worldwide to offer 11+ billion endpoints.</strong></div>
          <div class="tl-tags">
            <span class="tl-tag">Open Banking</span>
            <span class="tl-tag">Remittance</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tl-item tl-sp reveal rd3">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">2020 — 2024</div>
          <div class="tl-company">SadaPay</div>
          <div class="tl-role">IC &rarr; Senior &rarr; Lead &rarr; Head of Product Design</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">Pakistan's largest digital wallet. First in-house designer — grew with the company over 4 years. Built the design system connected to production code. Scaled team from <strong>1 to 12 designers.</strong> Led service design that reduced fraud. Product helped secure <strong>$20M+ in funding and a $50M acquisition by Papara.</strong></div>
          <div class="tl-tags">
            <span class="tl-tag">Design System</span>
            <span class="tl-tag">Team Building</span>
            <span class="tl-tag">Service Design</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tl-item tl-xp reveal">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">2020</div>
          <div class="tl-company">Xpence</div>
          <div class="tl-role">Product Designer &middot; VentureDive</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">Smart business spend platform for the UAE. Built an atomic design system in weeks. Designed the core experience.</div>
          <div class="tl-tags">
            <span class="tl-tag">B2B Fintech</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tl-item tl-wtt reveal">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-date">2023 — 2024</div>
          <div class="tl-company">Walking the Talk / ZRG</div>
          <div class="tl-role">Consultant Product Designer</div>
          <div class="tl-desc">Culture transformation platform for 200+ organizations across 40+ countries. Acquired by ZRG Partners — designed multiple products end-to-end across both brands.</div>
          <div class="tl-tags">
            <span class="tl-tag">Enterprise</span>
            <span class="tl-tag">Behavior Change</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="philosophy reveal">
      <div class="section-label">How I Think</div>
      <div class="phil-grid">
        <div class="phil-card reveal rd1">
          <div class="phil-num">01</div>
          <div class="phil-title">User-first, always</div>
          <div class="phil-text">Trust is hard to build and easy to lose.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phil-card reveal rd2">
          <div class="phil-num">02</div>
          <div class="phil-title">Systems over screens</div>
          <div class="phil-text">Tokens, governance, blueprints. The stuff nobody sees.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phil-card reveal rd3">
          <div class="phil-num">03</div>
          <div class="phil-title">Simplicity is the hardest work</div>
          <div class="phil-text">If it feels obvious, I did my job.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phil-card reveal rd4">
          <div class="phil-num">04</div>
          <div class="phil-title">Trust through craft</div>
          <div class="phil-text">Polish isn't decoration. It's a signal.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phil-card reveal rd5">
          <div class="phil-num">05</div>
          <div class="phil-title">Ship, then polish</div>
          <div class="phil-text">80% shipped beats 100% in Figma.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phil-card reveal rd6">
          <div class="phil-num">06</div>
          <div class="phil-title">Study what shipped</div>
          <div class="phil-text">Wise, Airbnb, Stripe. Not Dribbble.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="leadership reveal">
      <div class="section-label">Leadership</div>
      <div class="lead-quote">
        My role isn't to have all the answers. It's to ask the right questions, remove blockers, set the bar high, and
        <span class="lq-em">get out of the way.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lead-body">
        <p>I believe in empowerment over micromanagement. The designers I've led — some now at Revolut, some building their own startups — will tell you: I trust my team to own their work.</p>
        <p>I create systems so people can succeed independently. I push for craft culture while celebrating individual growth.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="testimonials reveal">
    <div class="trow trow-left">
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"SadaPay was praised for how well designed the product is — this is thanks to <strong>Basit</strong> and the exceptional product design team he built."</div><div class="ta">Brandon Timinsky</div><div class="tt">CEO, SadaPay &amp; ZAR</div></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"Under <strong>Basit's</strong> leadership of our design team, we were able to achieve this both consistently, and at a high level. I considered him our Head of Design, and one of my peers."</div><div class="ta">Eli Mydlarz</div><div class="tt">Head of Engineering, SadaPay</div></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"He added value from day one. He's a <strong>fearless problem solver</strong> and moves the needle whenever he enters a room."</div><div class="ta">Batsi Madzonga</div><div class="tt">Head of Design, ADIB</div></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"<strong>Basit</strong> is an insanely good UX designer. He has a keen eye for detail, delight, simplicity, and a deep focus on users and customers."</div><div class="ta">Sergio Sch&uuml;ler</div><div class="tt">Head of Product, SadaPay</div></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"SadaPay was praised for how well designed the product is — this is thanks to <strong>Basit</strong> and the exceptional product design team he built."</div><div class="ta">Brandon Timinsky</div><div class="tt">CEO, SadaPay &amp; ZAR</div></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"Under <strong>Basit's</strong> leadership of our design team, we were able to achieve this both consistently, and at a high level. I considered him our Head of Design, and one of my peers."</div><div class="ta">Eli Mydlarz</div><div class="tt">Head of Engineering, SadaPay</div></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"He added value from day one. He's a <strong>fearless problem solver</strong> and moves the needle whenever he enters a room."</div><div class="ta">Batsi Madzonga</div><div class="tt">Head of Design, ADIB</div></div>
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"<strong>Basit</strong> is an insanely good UX designer. He has a keen eye for detail, delight, simplicity, and a deep focus on users and customers."</div><div class="ta">Sergio Sch&uuml;ler</div><div class="tt">Head of Product, SadaPay</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="trow trow-right">
      <div class="tcard"><div class="tq">"His design decisions were always grounded in thorough analysis and strong rationale. He articulated insights in a clear and structured manner."</div><div class="ta">Daniel Young</div><div class="tt">Head of Digital Products &amp; Design, ADIB</div></div>
